name: Psychedelic Interference
description:
Created with Hydra Code and internal mixer feedback. Feeding the laptop with code into the chain of mixers and playing around (Edirol V4 into the Panasonic MX50). Rescanned off a RCA CRT monitor with a digital camera and ediited in Final Cut Pro. 

31 Second Video clip. 1920 x 1920 pixels.
